What is a text editor?

What is an IDE?

Multiple cursors
	- Vertical selector
	- Selecting multiple instances of the same text
	- Find every instance of the word "yup" in the phrase:
		"Yup, I think I'm going to enjoy this class. Yup, it'll definitely cover a lot. And yup,
		it won't be easy."

		- Select one at a time
			"command + d" on Mac - "ctrl + d" on Windows
		- Select all
			"control + command + g" on Mac - "Alt + F3" on Windows

Sidebar to scroll

Adjust size
	command + or command -

